PrecisAmendments to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL REGULATIONS which broaden the definition of "other interested parties" to include any association representing the interests of consumers in Canada, require that the various notification procedures apply to surge inquiries, and for the purposes of commencing such an inquiry, the Trubunal take into account specific factors.

precis:
Amendments to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL REGULATIONS
which broaden the definition of "other interested parties" to include any
association representing the interests of consumers in Canada, require that
the various notification procedures apply to surge inquiries, and for the
purposes of commencing such an inquiry, the Trubunal take into account
specific factors.
